<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure19>
    dc:description "Figure 19. Protoptilum stet. CCZ _ 068 A in situ image B whole colony C detail of polyps before preservation. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 5 mm (B); 2 mm (C). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716345" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure20>
    dc:description "Figure 20. Rooted Bayesian phylogeny of Ceriantharia. Concatenated (12 S, 16 S, 18 S, 28 S, and COI) median consensus BEAST tree with posterior probability (PP) and bootstrap (BS) values indicated. Only values of PP> 0.70 and BS> 50 are shown, with values of PP> 0.95 and BS> 90 indicated with a circle. Nodes not recovered on the RAxML tree are indicated with a hyphen. Sequences generated in this study are highlighted in violet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716346" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure21>
    dc:description "Figure 21. Spirularia stet. CCZ _ 067 A in situ image B specimen before preservation. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 2 mm (B). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716347" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure22>
    dc:description "Figure 22. Rooted Bayesian phylogeny of Scyphozoa. Concatenated (16 S, 18 S, 28 S, and COI) median consensus BEAST tree with posterior probability (PP) and bootstrap (BS) values indicated. Only values of PP> 0.70 and BS> 50 are shown, with values of PP> 0.95 and BS> 90 indicated with a circle. Nodes not recovered on the RAxML tree are indicated with a hyphen. Sequences generated in this study are highlighted in violet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716348" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure23>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Ulmaridae stet. CCZ _ 069 A in situ image B specimen before preservation C rhopalia. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 5 mm (B). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716349" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure24>
    dc:description "Figure 24. Rooted Bayesian phylogeny of Asteroidea. Concatenated (12 S, 16 S, 18 S, COI, and H 3) median consensus BEAST tree with posterior probability (PP) and bootstrap (BS) values indicated. Only values of PP> 0.70 and BS> 50 are shown, with values of PP> 0.95 and BS> 90 indicated with a circle. Nodes not recovered on the RAxML tree are indicated with a hyphen. Sequences generated in this study are highlighted in violet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716350" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

